<br><br>&nbsp;Acanthosis nigricans is often related to insulin levels in the body. For this reason, acanthosis nigricans may possibly signal that a person has prediabetes or diabetes.
<br><br>&nbsp;However, acanthosis nigricans has other known causes like birth control pills, hormonal disorders, corticosteroids, and other medications.
 

